Apple today revealed a number of updates for <a href="https://www.macrumors.com/guide/image-playground/">Image Playground</a> and <a href="https://www.macrumors.com/guide/genmoji/">Genmoji</a>.<br/>
<br/>
<img src="https://images.macrumors.com/article-new/2025/06/image-playground-26.jpg" alt="" width="1600" height="900" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1004966" /><br/>
ChatGPT image generation is now available directly in &zwnj;Image Playground&zwnj;, with new ChatGPT styles, such as Oil Painting, Vector, Anime, Print, and Watercolor. There is also a new &zwnj;Image Playground&zwnj; API for developers to use.<br/>
<br/>
Text descriptions can now be turned into a &zwnj;Genmoji&zwnj;, and two emojis can be combined. There are more options to customize Genmojis of people with different hairstyles and expressions.<br/>
